channel.author: Gareth Emery
channel.itunes:author: Gareth Emery
channel.itunes:subtitle: Archive of the entire original podcast
channel.itunes:summary: An archive of the Gareth Emery podcast which was first broadcast in March 2006. This podcast has been nominated for Best Podcast at the Miami Winter Music Conference's International Dance Music Awards three times. In November 2014, Emery announced that Episode 310 would be the final episode of the Gareth Emery Podcast. Its spiritual successor is the Electric For Life podcast which was also created by Gareth Emery. This podcast was removed from its original host which made it difficult for nostalgic fans to listen to. Finally, it is available within iTunes once again for all to enjoy Gareth's masterful mixes.
